msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"Battery has reached critical level. This notification triggers a countdown "
"before doing the configured action, hence it is strongly advised to leave it "
"on."
msgstr ""
"Vaša batéria dosiahla kritickú úroveň nabitia. Toto upozornenie spustí "
"odpočítavanie pred vykonaním prednastavenej akcie, preto je vysoko "
"doporučené nechať ho zapnuté."

